parameters:
\SE\SE[15]Oh my, everyone! \SE[15]Do you happen to need any
lovely accessories or something like that?!

These blocks here are bouncing stones. Hey, would you like to try
a jump too, miss?

I heard that the amazing jumper can perform the legendary 4th
jump. Do you know what that means, big sister?

...I was watching. When big sister landed the quadruple jump... I
couldn't help but acknowledge her as a skilled jumper.
Take this. You should have it more than I do.

Your jump is truly amazing. It's very inspiring for us as well...
Although the sound is a little concerning...

I wonder how many times I can jump today! Damn it... I'm getting
addicted to it...!

Ulyssean Swordsmanship ~ Beginners Welcome ~ Dojo Invaders also
Welcome!

This kind of jump... it doesn't have any meaning, but... for some
reason, I just can't help but do it...

I am guarding the castle gate. Please leave if you have no
business here.

The torch next to me is so hot... I feel like I'm turning into a
steamed octopus inside this armor...

Are you here for official business within the castle? I'm sorry,
but please leave.
Orolo...!! Ugh... I drank too much... Orolo...!!

I am on duty! It is mandatory to have security guards stationed
at the weapons trading post!

Today is a wonderful day... The flowers are blooming. The birds
are chirping...

If you'd like! How about staying overnight?! My mom's cooking is
delicious, you know!

I... drank too much alcohol... Let me rest for a little... just a
little...

Having stairs on the walking course really makes a difference.
It's like the quality of the day improves...

I'm struggling in life! Love will surely save the world!! Please,
take the first step and extend a helping hand too! ... It seems
like I'm receiving money from people passing by.

Ugh... I drank too much... Ahh... This is bad. I'm going to die.
Me.

How about worshiping the gods of Ulyssean? If you're willing, how
about making an offering as well?

It seems like the cat's business tools. Various things seem to be
packed inside...

Sometimes there is a misunderstanding... There are plenty of
people in Ulyssean who get married just like anyone else.
I came to this country just because I like girls.

\SE[2]... According to the information, this place is... Yone,
right? \SE[3] Knowing that person, it's probably correct, but...

\SE\SE[75]To be honest, I have some concerns about our combat
capabilities... \SE[3]There's no guarantee that we won't keep
searching for this route forever... \SE[75]I guess we have no
choice but to give up...

\SE[58]Sigh... I'm definitely going to get wet. \SE[75]That's
what's most depressing...
\SE[95]Ugh... I've been separated from Lunaroa again...

\SE[51]Will we never be able to meet again in the future...?
\!\SM[tremble]\SE[52]Ah... that's impossible... I'll die from
loneliness...
\SE[95]If something like that were to happen... I, I...

\SE[10]Ugh... What should I do? \!\SE[53]I wonder what I should
do...?
\SM[rock]\SE[50]Ah, what's that...? I'm feeling a bit dizzy...?
\SE[88]Ugh... It feels like a lot has happened...

\SE\SE[0]Hehe... But I'm glad we were able to meet up safely.
\SE[0]It's still before noon, but what should we do from here?

\SE[2]Should we look for a place to stay? \!\SE[5]But I don't
have that much money...

\SE[3]Money... That's right. \SM[nod]\SE[33]Certainly, we need to
stabilize our income and expenses as soon as possible...

\SE[2]It might be a little early, but... \!\SE[0]How about the
two of us try taking on a quest from the Guild?

\SE\SE[0]Even people like us, refugees and adventurers, can earn
income. \SE[0]The Guild provides job referrals for that purpose.

\SE[3]There might be some dangerous jobs as well... \!\SE[1]If
Laura doesn't want to, I can take them on alone...

\SE[12]There's no way I'm leaving everything to Luna alone!
\SM[double]\SE[17]I'm going too! \SE[60]Absolutely going!!

\SE[0] (...I shouldn't have done that. \!\SE[45]I couldn't help
but say something like that.)
\SE[86]I wonder if everyone in the surviving village is okay...?

\SE[3]I can't say for sure... \!\SM[nod]\SE[0]But I did inform
the important people in Yurisine. \!\SE[1]They said they will
create a search party and look for them.

\SE\SE[15]So for now, let's focus on our own worries.
\SE[15]Don't worry, I'm sure everyone is safe.

\SM[nod]\SE[100]Hmm... I got it! \!\SE[16]Alright, let's go to
the Guild! \!\SE[17]We have to be able to take care of ourselves,
after all!

\SE\SE[0]I'm glad. Laura seems to be feeling better. \SE[0]How
about we take a tour of the town and see various things? \SE[2]I
think there should be some places nearby.
Hey, you two...! It seems like you're looking for the Guild, huh?

Well, you're in luck! The Guild is on the left, right here!! It's
good that you won't get lost now!

\SE\SE[0]Thank you very much for your kindness. \SE[0]Thanks to
you, I was saved.
Don't worry! Since you're here, I'll guide you casually!

First, this is the Weapon and Armor Shop!! The Soldier at the
entrance is the landmark! First, let's start with the
equipment...! Anyway, it's good to take a look!

But recently, it seems like we're being pushed by someone called
Uber... something or other!

The 'Tavern'! The drunken 'scum' is the landmark!! \! But there's
nothing particularly essential about it!

This is the Item Shop over here! \! They sell recovery items, so
if you're feeling uneasy, you should go and check it out!

Here as well, we're on the verge of going out of business because
of someone called Uber... something or other! So, there's no need
to go there!

This is the Inn! \! At first glance, it may seem important... but
in reality, it has no meaning at all! \! Returning to Yurisene
will fully restore you!

Even though it's such a sad facility, I love the cute children
who are summoned! \!... It does have meaning after all! \. I'm
glad!

So, that's the general idea! In other words, the facilities on
the lower level are completely unnecessary! Oh, and something
else you should know...

It seems like a Refugee Protection Facility has been established
here! War and looting are really the worst, aren't they?! Ugh!
The flow of the world is so heartless. It's really tough!!

Well, something like this? \! Well then, I'm in a hurry, so see
you later. \. Bye!
\SE[21] Ahaha... You're quite energetic, aren't you?

\SE[8]I was a little worried, but... \SE[28]If there are such
kind people like this, maybe I can manage somehow...?
